{
  "info": {
    "name": "OCP — Progress Module",
    "description": "Online Course Platform — Progress Module API\n\nPhase 3: Хэрэглэгчийн хичээл тус бүрийн ахиц хянах, сургалтын нийт явцыг тооцоолох\n\n## Хэрэглэх дараалал\n1. Auth → Student, Teacher, Admin нэвтрэх\n2. Setup → Сургалт + хичээлүүд үүсгэх + нийтлэх + элсэлт\n3. Progress → Update → Position → Get → Complete → Auto-complete enrollment → Delete\n\n## Урьдчилсан нөхцөл\n- DB-д STUDENT, TEACHER, ADMIN role-тэй хэрэглэгчид бүртгэлтэй байх\n- Published сургалт + published хичээлүүд байх\n- Student элсэлт ACTIVE байх\n\n## Variables\n- `baseUrl`: API URL (default: http://localhost:3001/api/v1)\n- `studentToken`: STUDENT JWT\n- `teacherToken`: TEACHER JWT\n- `adminToken`: ADMIN JWT\n- `courseId`: Published сургалтын ID\n- `videoLessonId`: VIDEO хичээлийн ID\n- `textLessonId`: TEXT хичээлийн ID\n- `progressId`: Ахицын ID",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3001/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "studentToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "teacherToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "courseId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "videoLessonId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "textLessonId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "progressId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01. Auth — Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Student",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('studentToken', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.test('Student token saved', () => pm.expect(res.data.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"progress-student@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Pass1234!\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Progress\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Student\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
